      "content": "thanks. i looked at the rules and they seem pretty standard, so i'm thinking about pushing an update to the detection engine to tune down the sensitivity on those specific patterns. if i deploy a patch to smooth out these false positives, do you see any potential issues with the detection accuracy during the transition?",
